{"tid":1010972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佈告出爐　香港只屬於「部分自由」地方　59分　比印尼和菲律賓差","createTime":"2019-02-06T11:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T18:08:54.000Z","uid":47714,"like":101,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2f922700091eb2846d0938669d3f2fb31772d1","tid":1010972,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=495710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D495710&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=a2cb3745\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D495710&h=9d34c383\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=495710</a><br />\n<br />\n根據美國民間獨立機構「自由之家」(Freedom House)日前公布2019世界自由度調查報告，芬蘭、挪威和瑞典均獲得滿分100，並列自由國家之冠，而台灣獲得93分，並列26位，被評比為「自由」的國家；而中國僅拿到11分，被評為「不自由」國家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/05/1770361-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F05%2F1770361-XXL.jpg&h=a8cb2ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲根據世界自由度調查台灣得分已優於美國、南韓。（圖／翻攝自Freedom House自由度調查報告）<br />\n<br />\n報告評估的195個國家中，86國被評為「自由」，59國被評為「部份自由」，還有50國為「不自由」。但值得玩味的，在國人印象中，常以美國民主做為典範，但這份報告卻指出，美國民主雖依然強勁，但過去8年，美國的民主被嚴重削弱，100分評分中獲得86分，低於法國、德國、英國等民主大國，更低於台灣的93分。<br />\n<br />\n在亞洲國家部分，被評為「自由」的國家中，日本96分，位居第12，是亞洲最高得分國家，南韓則低於台灣，獲83分，蒙古85分、印度75分。<br />\n<br />\n被評比為「部分自由」的亞洲國家中，印尼62分、菲律賓61、香港59分、馬來西亞52分、新加坡51分、緬甸30分；被評比為「不自由」的亞洲國家中，泰國30分、越南20分、寮國14分、中國11分、北韓3分、西藏則被自由之家評比只有1分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/05/1770360-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F05%2F1770360-XXL.jpg&h=336e62c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲根據世界自由度調查中國僅拿到11分，被評為「不自由」國家。（圖／翻攝自Freedom House自由度調查報告）<br />\n<br />\n該報告指出，全球自由度連續第13年下降，不論是美國，還是中國、俄羅斯這類專制政權，民主退潮。以日漸強勢的中國為代表，越來越多專制國家把旅居海外和流亡海外人士作為靶子。近來，全球有24個國家利用騷擾、引渡要求、綁架甚至謀殺等手段，針對海外政治異見人士；報告更批評中國把維吾爾族關進「再教育營」，並針對海外異見人士，將全球變成間諜和刺客的狩獵場。"},{"pid":"bcdb8652b61624c2c281413f2d36f012c8d8b506","tid":1010972,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82eb4c8568b6a7cc01e76092d22b5bf42dcc87ec","tid":1010972,"uid":6604,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"又講錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea73905c4c5c2471ded277e7fe3fbca3a306762","tid":1010972,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":41,"score":-39,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"差過菲律賓又有點誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebc05c64ae3394a0c01f1aa11fde00723549e14","tid":1010972,"uid":47080,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"quote":{"pid":"cea73905c4c5c2471ded277e7fe3fbca3a306762","tid":1010972,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":41,"score":-39,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"差過菲律賓又有點誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"講自由喎，差過菲律賓真係唔奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad09b6bacd49681ac0c5c1c4df9e8ab42396436","tid":1010972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905315f7e1fa38407bbd212af0b8ecb9d05f7c14","tid":1010972,"uid":92376,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"泰國30<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gi